- Build within existing trusted ecosystems (Miceli Social, La Fundici√≥)
- Don't impose external solutions, introduce gradually
- Leverage established relationships
- Enable organic spread through trust networks

### Cosmo-Local Integration
- Global resources + local knowledge
- Traditional Catalan cooperative values + Web3 tools
- Create templates for global adaptation while serving local needs

### Depth Over Breadth
- 12 carefully curated projects (not 50+)
- Comprehensive support: funding + capacity building + mentorship
- Generate visible success stories

